snippet.title: Ashwalkers: A Survival Journey - Switch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
7 months after Ashwalkers' PC release we have the pleasure to announce that a Switch version (digital and physical) is coming Q1 2022 

In partnership with @MeridiemGames a Survivor Edition for the Physical Release will be available!

All the link here: https://linktr.ee/ashwalkers
